Package: trajr
Type: Package
Title: Trajectory Analysis in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Jim", "McLean", email = "jim.mclean@optusnet.com.au",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A toolbox to assist with statistical analysis of 2-dimensional animal trajectories. 
    It provides simple access to algorithms for calculating and assessing a variety of characteristics 
    such as speed and acceleration, as well as multiple measures of straightness or tortuosity.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/JimMcL/trajr
BugReports: https://github.com/JimMcL/trajr/issues
